NUMBER 2437
NAME The Top of the Tree
CALL 33
CHANNEL 669
*DESCRIPTION_START
The sturdy branches here are tightly woven together as they curve upward, forming a natural latticework bowl in which you now stand. An aelfen guard of implacable demeanor stands silent watch over a mysterious doorway. To the south the open area continues. A narrow stairway winds down, behind the massive trunk and out of view. A small crystal plate hangs from a low branch.
*DESCRIPTION_END
REGION 151
FOREST
FIXED_LIGHT
ITEM 0 1341 ADJ1=209  VAL2=2438
EXTEND 0 with a stern-faced and motionless guard beside it
ITEM 3 607  ADJ1=1225
EXTEND 3 just within reach
ITEM 1 1226 ADJ1=210 VAL2=2443
EXTEND 1 winding down and around the trunk of the massive tree
ITEM 2 1592 ADJ1=294 ADJ2=77
EXTEND 2 cracked down the center, spidery lines winding their way along its surface
ITEM 9 693
EXIT D 2436
EXIT S 2441
IFSAY Guards!
 IFVAR ORG = 27
  EQUAL RITUALVAL2 351
  SPELL 2
  ECHO ALL The grayshroud snaps to attention!
  ECHO PLAYER The guard asks, "What is thy bidding my master?"
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFENTRY
 IFVAR ARENADEATH = 1
  ECHO PLAYER The guards deposit your limp body gently on the ground.
  ECHO OTHERS The guards deposit %n's limp body gently on the ground.
 ELSE
  IFVAR ORG = 27
   IFVAR GEN = 0
    ECHO PLAYER The guard salutes you and says,"Dagas Elui %n!"
    ECHO OTHERS The guard salutes %n and says, "Dagas Elui!       
   ENDIF
   IFVAR GEN = 1
    ECHO PLAYER The guard salutes you and says,"Dagas Alui %n!"
    ECHO OTHERS The guard salutes %n and says, "Dagas Alui!" 
   ENDIF
  ELSE
   IFCARRY 1861 -1
    IFITEM -1 WORN
     ECHO PLAYER The guard greets you with a friendly nod.
     ECHO OTHERS The guard greets %n with a friendly nod.
    ELSE
     ECHO PLAYER The guard reminds you to wear your shroud at all times in the tree.
     ECHO OTHERS The guard has some harsh words with %n.
    ENDIF
   ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The guard eyes you warily.
    ECHO OTHERS The guard eyes %n warily.
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB SEARCH -1
 ECHO PLAYER %cYou notice a sturdy branch just within reach.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB DOWN -1
 IFVAR ORG ! 27
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER A grey-shrouded guard steps in front of you and says, "Non-Members may not leave that way. You'll have to use the other route."
  ECHO OTHERS A grey-shrouded guard steps in front of you and says, "Non-Members may not leave that way. You'll have to use the other route."
  ECHO ALL The grey-shrouded guard gestures at a sturdy branch that hangs just within reach.
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER The guard gives you a subtle nod as you pass.
  ECHO OTHERS The guard nods to %n.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CLIMB 3
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You reach out and grab %a.%cYou pull yourself up higher into the tree.
 ECHO OTHERS %n grabs onto %a and pulls %i self higher into the tree.
 DISBAND
 MOVE 3758
 AFFECT 3758
 ECHO PLAYER You emerge at the very roof of the forest itself.
 ECHO OTHERS %n climbs up from below.
 AFFECT 2437
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 0
 DISBAND
 IFVAR RAC = 2
  IFVAR TEIWAZPASS ! 1
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The guard steps in front of you to bar your way.
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER The guard steps aside, allowing you to enter.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  IFVAR ORG = 27
   IFVAR TEIWAZPASS ! 1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The guard steps in front of you to bar your way.
   ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The guard steps aside, allowing you to enter.
   ENDIF
  ELSE
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER The guard steps in front of you, saying, "You must be a guild member, or a true aelfen to enter."
   ECHO OTHERS The guard steps in front of %n, saying, "You must be a guild member, or a true aelfen to enter."
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
