   SPELL 2 0
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER Due to your affinity to your totem, you have learned to call the animals of the woodlands...
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER ...You call out to the creatures of the wood, trying desperately to imitate the Aelfen lilt you have heard so many times...
   ECHO OTHERS %n's features almost look Aelfen as %s calls out in a lilting musical language...
