NUMBER 2438
NAME The Challenge Room
CALL 33
ECHOCHAN 669
ARENA
ASTRAL
REGION 151
*DESCRIPTION_START
Within the embrace of the mighty trunk of the tree, you stand in the center of a great circular chamber. The walls are formed of the living wood of the tree itself. The floor is covered in a concentric ring pattern, which is centered perfectly in the middle of the chamber. It has been worn to a velvet smoothness by the tread of feet over the ages. Of the door through which you entered you can see no sign.
*DESCRIPTION_END
DROPLOC 2437
FIXED_LIGHT
IFLOGIN
 ECHO PLAYER The guards escort you out of the chamber.
 ECHO OTHERS The guards escort %n out of the chamber.
 MOVE 2437
ENDIF
IFENTRY
 EQUAL TCHALLENGE 1
 EQUAL TEIWAZPASS 0
 PLREVENT 2
 CONTPLREVENT
 IFCARRY 1861 -1
  IFVAR ITEMVAL5 < 50
   ECHO ALL  A warrior wearing a silver shroud leaps to his feet and advances towards you.
   GENMON 350
   EQUAL TCHALLENGE 2
  ELSE
   IFVAR ITEMVAL5 < 100 
    ECHO ALL A warrior wearing a gray shroud leaps to his feet and advances towards you.
    GENMON 351
    EQUAL TCHALLENGE 2
   ELSE
    ECHO ALL A warrior wearing a black shroud leaps to his feet and advances towards you.
    GENMON 352
    EQUAL TCHALLENGE 2
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO ALL A warrior wearing a white shroud steps forth and bows towards %n.
  GENMON 349
  EQUAL TCHALLENGE 2
 ENDIF
ENDIF
