NUMBER 2439
NAME Within the Roots
CALL 33
INDOOR_GROUND
REGION 151
*DESCRIPTION_START
The roots of the giant oak weave their skein in a dizzying pattern of latticework which thrusts deep into the rich soil all around you. This subterranean hollow lays directly beneath the trunk of the great oak. A circular fire pit rests in the precise center of the chamber. The only obvious egress would be to climb through the tangle of roots back into the boughs of the tree. A dark opening leads along a wide transverse root into another cavern.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1629 
EXTEND 0 that are interlocked in a intricate and tangled skein
ITEM 1 1398 ADJ1=126
EXTEND 1 that lays in the very center of the chamber
ITEM 2 72 ADJ1=87 VAL2=2445
EXTEND 2 leading along a wide transverse root
ITEM 9 693
IFPREVERB GO 0
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You seem to become one with the roots of the tree as they envelop you...
 ECHO OTHERS The roots open up to envelop %n, and then %s is gone.
 MOVE 2442
 AFFECT 2442
 ECHO OTHERS %n walks out of the bark of the tree!
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 2
 IFVAR ORG ! 27
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER A guard steps in front of you and says,"Non-Members may not go there without a member to accompany them."
  ECHO OTHERS A guard steps in front of %n and says,"Non-Members may not go there without a member to accompany them."
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 1
 CLEARVERB
 IFCARRY 1861 -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
   IFVAR TEIWAZPITLIT = 2
    IFVAR FLAG3 = 3
     ECHO PLAYER You step forward into the embrace of the swirling smoke...
     ECHO OTHERS %n's body goes still.
     MOVE 2440
     AFFECT 2440
     ECHO OTHERS An ethereal representation of %n arrives.
    ELSE
     ECHO PLAYER You are not yet prepared to do that.
    ENDIF
   ELSE
    ECHO PLAYER The fire pit has not been prepared.
   ENDIF
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER You realize you do not have the protection of your shroud.
   ECHO OTHERS %n looks down at the shroud in %h hands with embarrassment.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 999 As you step into the fire pit the flames lick at your body!
  ECHO OTHERS %n screams in pain as %s steps into the fire!
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LIGHT 1
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR TEIWAZPITLIT = 0
  EQUAL TEIWAZPITLIT 1      
  ECHO PLAYER You carefully ignite the kindling within the pit...
  ECHO OTHERS %N carefully ignites the kindling within the pit...
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL ...The pleasant aroma of freshly lit mirmach fills your nostrils.
  PLREVENT 2 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The flames begin to lick higher and higher as the fuel within the pit is consumed...
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The heat of the flames bathes your face in its warm embrace...
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The fire begins to rage in the chamber, contained only by the damp soil of its walls.
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL With an audible "snap!" the last logs tumble into the flames sending a dazzling shower of sparks high into the air!
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The burning embers give way to glowing coals as smoke begins to pour out of the smoldering pit...
  EQUAL TEIWAZPITLIT 2
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The wondrous smell of the smoldering bark fills the entire area, intoxicating you with a strange lighteadedness...
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL Your head begins to spin slightly as your lungs fill with the pleasant smelling smoke...
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL Your eyes grow heavy with the euphoria of the smoldering bark...%c>%c...Your eyes close.
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL You feel your spirit straining to be free within its cage of flesh as the aromatic smoke dissolves your mortal bonds...
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL You receive a series of strange visions... both future and past... perhaps some present...
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The visions fade slowly as the last of the embers dies away.
  PLREVENT 3 
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The smoke clears as the pit begins to grow cold.
  EQUAL TEIWAZPITLIT 0
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER The fire already burns within the pit.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB KNEEL -1
 IFVAR POSITION ! 3
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You kneel Aelfen fashion and rest your hands upturned upon your knees, curled in the ancient handsigns of nobility and life.
  ECHO OTHERS %n kneels Aelfen fashion and rests %h hands upturned upon %h knees, curled in the ancient handsigns of nobility and life.
  POSITION KNEEL
  EQUAL FLAG3 1
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SMELL -1
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR FLAG3 = 1
  IFVAR TEIWAZPITLIT = 2
   ECHO PLAYER You close your eyes and take a deep breath, inhaling the pleasant scents of the smoldering bark.
   ECHO OTHERS %n takes a series of long, deep breaths, exhaling with a sigh.
   PLREVENT 1
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER Your spirit grows light as does your head with the euphoria of the smoldering bark.
   EQUAL FLAG3 2
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER You inhale the damp aroma of the soil.
   ECHO OTHERS %n takes a deep breath.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER You inhale the damp aroma of the soil.
  ECHO OTHERS %n takes a deep breath.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB STAND -1
 IFVAR POSITION = 3
  IFVAR FLAG3 = 2
   IFVAR TEIWAZPITLIT = 2
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You slowly rise, realizing that you have left your body behind you...
    ECHO OTHERS The swirling smoke in the chamber seems to outline a humanoid form, rising out of %n's body.
    POSITION STAND
    EQUAL FLAG3 3
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
