NUMBER 2440
NAME The Dreaming
OUTOFBODY
CALL 33
CHANNEL 100
FOREST
REGION 151
*DESCRIPTION_START
An endless vista of tall, dark trees fills the land in all directions. As far as you can see the forest continues in its full and primal glory. The sounds and smells of the forest seem clearer to you than ever before. You are certain that you can actually feel every blade of grass, every insect and every being within this vista as if it were your own embodiment. A narrow footpath, worn smooth by the animals of the forest leads off into the trees.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 9 693
IFVERB LISTEN -1
 PLREVENT 1
 CONTPLREVENT
 ECHO PLAYER You hear the rustling of leaves as some animal moves past you.
ENDIF
IFVERB SMELL -1
 PLREVENT 1
 CONTPLREVENT
 ECHO PLAYER You smell the fresh scent of pine mixing with the sweet scent of wild grasses.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB CALL -1
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR TEIWAZCALL = 0
  EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 1
  IFVAR INTNUM57 = 0
   ECHO PLAYER You send out a questing call to the spirits of the wood, trilling through a range of various animal sounds...
   ECHO OTHERS %n sends out a questing call to the spirits of the wood, trilling through a range of various animal sounds...
   STRCVT 0 INTNUM3
   STRCVT 1 PLAYERNUM
   GMMSG ** %n, Player #%1, with an Intnum3 of %0, has called for a totem.
   GMMSG ** VARIABLES TEIWAZNUM3 and TEIWAZTOTEM must now be set.
   GMMSG ** INTNUM57 = 1/wolf 2/raven 3/owl 4/falcon 5/eagle 6/deer 7/bat 8/boar 9/snake 10/cat.
   PLREVENT 3
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER You wait with serene patience as the atmosphere within the wood grows silent and pregnant with expectation...
   ECHO OTHERS The forest grows silent.
   PLREVENT 9 
   CONTPLREVENT 
   IFVAR INTNUM3 = TEIWAZNUM3
    EQUAL INTNUM57 TEIWAZTOTEM
    ECHO PLAYER You sense the touch and acceptance of a primal force.
    ECHO OTHERS %n is surrounded by an unseen presence!
   ELSE
    ECHO ALL The spirits of the wood seem not to respond.
   ENDIF
   EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 0
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER You call out in a primal tongue!
   ECHO OTHERS %n calls out in a primal tongue!
   IFVAR INTNUM57 = 1
    GMMSG ** %n has called Wolf in room 2440!
    PLREVENT 10
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Wolf steps out of the trees and nods to %n growling, "May your pack run strong, my cub."
    EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR INTNUM57 = 2
    GMMSG ** %n has called Raven in room 2440!
    PLREVENT 10
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Raven swoops out of the trees and nods to %n saying, "Greetings, hatchling, you have come to partake of my boundless cunning?"
    EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR INTNUM57 = 4
    GMMSG ** %n has called Falcon in room 2440!
    PLREVENT 10
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Falcon drops in from the air above and nods to %n saying, "May your strike be swift and sure, my hatchling."
    EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR INTNUM57 = 7
    GMMSG ** %n has called Bat in room 2440!
    PLREVENT 10
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Bat darts out of the sky and nods to %n saying, "May the depths of the night welcome you, my child."
    EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR INTNUM57 = 10
    GMMSG ** %n has called Cat in room 2440!
    PLREVENT 10
    CONTPLREVENT
    ECHO ALL Cat prowls out of the trees and nods to %n saying, "Patience is oft rewarded, my kit."
    EQUAL TEIWAZCALL 0
   ENDIF
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER You decide not to disturb the forest before it responds to the former call.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFSAY Chlry'est
 ECHO ALL The words ring through the forest!
 ECHO PLAYER You feel the sudden return of bodily sensations!
 ECHO OTHERS %n is suddenly gone.
 POSITION KNEEL
 MOVE 1469
 AFFECT 1469
 ECHO OTHERS %n's still body suddenly animates!
ENDIF
IFSAY ABASTOLI_IENNA
 ECHO ALL The words ring through the forest!
 ECHO PLAYER You feel the sudden return of bodily sensations!
 ECHO OTHERS %n is suddenly gone.
 POSITION KNEEL
 MOVE 2439
 AFFECT 2439
 ECHO OTHERS %n's still body suddenly animates!
ENDIF
