NUMBER 2442
NAME Treetop, Terrace
CALL 33
REGION 151
*DESCRIPTION_START
You stand atop an open terrace of interlocking branches and boughs. Above you the sky spans out like a blanket of blue velvet and the smells, sights and sounds of the forest fills your every sense. The the southeast, just above the treetops you can spy a few scattered plumes of smoke rising from the rooftops of Fayd and the Arcana tower, rising behind the forest like a weavers needle. To the northwest the Teeth of Shartan rise out of the ground and you realize exactly how they got their name. For they perfectly resemble a set of jagged and ferocious fangs. Two beautifully carven chairs have been set out here for relaxing. To the northeast, an arch of interlacing branches leads back into the tree.
*DESCRIPTION_END
FOREST
FIXED_LIGHT
ITEM 0 229 
;TREE
ITEM 1 86
EXTEND 1 carven with sturdy looking lions feet
ITEM 9 693
IFPREVERB GO 0
 IFCARRY 1861 -1
  IFITEM -1 WORN
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You step directly into the tree becoming one with it and traveling within its roots!
   ECHO OTHERS %n steps directly into the tree and vanishes!
   MOVE 2439
   AFFECT 2439
   ECHO OTHERS %n steps out from a tangle of roots.
  ELSE
   CLEARVERB
   ECHO PLAYER You realize you are not wearing your shroud.
  ENDIF
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SNEAK -1
 IFVAR ORG ! 27
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER You can't seem to do that.
  ECHO OTHERS You notice %n acting rather suspicious.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GAZE -1
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You slowly turn yourself in a circle, fully appreciating the beauty around you.
 ECHO OTHERS %n turns slowly in a circle, fully appreciating the beauty around %i.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB SNIFF -1
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You take a deep breath, the aroma's of the forest filling your nostrils. 
 ECHO OTHERS %n takes a deep breath and exhales with a sigh.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB RECALL -1
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER You recall nothing of this area, yet, just being here fills you with a sense of awe and wonder for the world around you.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LISTEN -1
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER The wondrous sounds of the living forest fill your ears, enchanting you momentarily.
 ECHO OTHERS %n closes %h eyes and listens to the living forest around %i.
ENDIF
