Totems, covering an entire wall. In one corner is a small workbench 
where the beginnings of a bow can be seen.  Next to the large desk, 
a wine rack of oiled rosewood seems well stocked.  Bookcases line 
another wall. You notice some of the books look exceedingly old and 
fragile. Several sturdy chairs and a leather sofa are here.
