*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The desk is littered with various weapons, elements of disguise and vials filled with what look like nasty looking stuff. Cleverly worked into the wood surface of the desk, you see a firing mechanism designed to fry anyone who touches it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB EXAM 3
 CLEARVERB
 ECHO PLAYER There are so many bottles of various types of wine, you don't know where to begin.
ENDIF
