STOREITEM 1985 241 700
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
This magnificent statue seem almost alive as it appears to step out of the limestone wall from which it has been formed. Skilled artisans have successfully captured the true essence of Deer in her towering form. Every feature has been shaped with delicate and painstaking intricacy, from the living limestone of the cavern wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
