IFSAY KREEBONKER_BITES!
 ECHO ALL You hear the sobbing of Kreebonker from the corner.
ELSE
 RANDOM DUMMY4 1 5 0
 IFVAR DUMMY4 > 3
  PLREVENT 0
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER Your voice echoes through the chamber.
  ECHO OTHERS %n's voice echoes through the chamber.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB GO 2
 CLEARVERB
 IFVAR WEALTH > 500
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 15
  ECHO PLAYER You hand five coins to the healer and lay down on the mat.
  ECHO OTHERS %n hands the healer some coins and lays down on her mat.
  SUB WEALTH 500
  POSITION LAY
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER The old woman passes her hands over your body, chanting melodically.
  ECHO OTHERS The old woman passes her hands over %n's body, chanting melodically.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO PLAYER She presses various herbs and bundled leaves into your wounds.
  ECHO OTHERS She presses various herbs and bundled leaves into %n's wounds.
  SPELL 318 0
  RANDOM DUMMY1 1 10 0
  ADD BODYPOINTS DUMMY1
  ECHO PLAYER You feel a bit better.
  PLREVENT 1
  CONTPLREVENT
  ECHO ALL The healer raises her gaze to the limestone statue and beseeches Deer for her aid.
  SPELL 342 0
  ECHO PLAYER A white aura flows from the healer's hands to surround your body.
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER The healer asks for five gold coins, and you realize you cannot pay her.  
  ECHO OTHERS %n speaks with the healer.
 ENDIF
ENDIF
