NUMBER 3452
NAME Beneath the Tree, Forge
CALL 33
CAVE
REGION 151
FORGE
*DESCRIPTION_START
This sheltered alcove just off the main cavern features a small forge and all the tools necessary for the smithing trade. The a webwork of cracks through the overhanging limestone ceiling provides ventilation for the dense, black smoke pouring out of the stoked forge. An archway leads back to the cavern itself.
*DESCRIPTION_END
