NUMBER 3453
NAME Beneath the Tree, Fletching
CAVE
CALL 33
REGION 151
FLETCHER
*DESCRIPTION_START
This comfortable nook off the main cavern holds all the tools and equipment necessary for the crafting of missile weapons of all types. A small table stand in the center of the room, for use in putting the finishing touches on your work. An archway leads back into the main cavern.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 0 1517
EXTEND 0 made out of hardened clay
