ITEM 9 693
IFPREVERB2 PUT 2
 IFVAR RAC = 2
  CLEARVERB
  EQUAL ROUNDTIME 10
  ECHO PLAYER You place the item on the table and work swiftly, giving it that distinctive aelfen look.
  ECHO OTHERS %n places something on the table and works swiftly, giving it that distinctive aelfen touch.
  IFVAR ITEMADJ1 < 1
   SETITEMADJ -1 1 1
   PLREVENT 3
   CONTPLREVENT
   ECHO PLAYER You retrieve the item from the table.
   ECHO OTHERS %n retrieves the item from the table.
  ELSE
   ECHO PLAYER That item cannot be altered.
  ENDIF
 ELSE
  ECHO PLAYER You place the item on the table, but do not know how to continue.
  ECHO OTHERS %n places an item on the table, but does not know how to continue.
 ENDIF
